&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;391&quot; data-backw=&quot;558&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/e7Jp2CicGtKCmLhmuw9zP2ttLNYribo9bA1CsicSn63zt4FXaWpRvH1sdI2Lw8HKj8UTWAmqgZKr6liaV8YUTWKXgA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/e7Jp2CicGtKCmLhmuw9zP2ttLNYribo9bA1CsicSn63zt4FXaWpRvH1sdI2Lw8HKj8UTWAmqgZKr6liaV8YUTWKXgA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;601&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;381.72821270310186&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6339434276206323&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xC7rrxMCrZND5eHRYgtLdSahZ3lNic0nAeSEjqK9IvXr5Fr0OcvfwUiaPbwsgRw8usky2q9OGCCDAmA/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;601&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;403&quot; data-backw=&quot;558&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/e7Jp2CicGtKCmLhmuw9zP2ttLNYribo9bAxNDLVoY4Z7TDygaMEKG84eicbxviaGWcqsHKAicJmuSCJlynt7OUmKlcA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/e7Jp2CicGtKCmLhmuw9zP2ttLNYribo9bAxNDLVoY4Z7TDygaMEKG84eicbxviaGWcqsHKAicJmuSCJlynt7OUmKlcA/640?wx_fmt=png&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;609&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;403.0014771048744&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.6617405582922824&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xC7rrxMCrZND5eHRYgtLdSawpKBzBxVYBI1UqBIic3lpW1UzWJdB1jFvibybffuHVSWvpr8I4436lfQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;609&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;昨天D&amp;amp;G创始人辱华事件引起广泛关注，微博热搜前9条全部都与此事相关。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;ins class=&quot;adsbygoogle&quot; data-ad-layout=&quot;in-article&quot; data-ad-format=&quot;fluid&quot; data-ad-client=&quot;ca-pub-1837452791782084&quot; data-ad-slot=&quot;7041996284&quot;&gt;&lt;/ins&gt; &lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;531&quot; data-backw=&quot;409&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/wZ8jfcVwf7I7TNS6LvxJ1pqYu9nHlTRSf2HPUKbc1KMvvoqbBGGice4n05icCKAzZzO3TAX4MBFkhW09d6yDUYDw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xC7rrxMCrZND5eHRYgtLdSa3HH1qQMWHb3L7nm5XvONuDs8NPCVJtGQiaKGrGy78P6lAHIo62Aic4OQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.2982885085574571&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xC7rrxMCrZND5eHRYgtLdSa3HH1qQMWHb3L7nm5XvONuDs8NPCVJtGQiaKGrGy78P6lAHIo62Aic4OQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;409&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9975&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/wZ8jfcVwf7I7TNS6LvxJ1pqYu9nHlTRStUvXG6HwY2xtJwJOE2MlOEsnITtxssu32XFqpWepu0S3ycpOO16r3A/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;400&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9981447124304267&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/wZ8jfcVwf7I7TNS6LvxJ1pqYu9nHlTRSowzV0ERYeG3Ru3fvukRhUJw9YOm8iav9gc2nicOu2S8zy8IerDPVJkEA/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;539&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;__bg_gif&quot; data-copyright=&quot;0&quot; data-ratio=&quot;0.9053803339517625&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/wZ8jfcVwf7I7TNS6LvxJ1pqYu9nHlTRSFJuCucwjTe0kNRBg2Ep7AKicYEus2U3fDBZGjxX159y9gwJGjQKJ8vQ/640?wx_fmt=gif&quot; data-type=&quot;gif&quot; data-w=&quot;539&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;在经历明星模特集体退出、“教科书级”灾难公关、大秀“改期”后，昨晚，该品牌大使迪丽热巴、王俊凯先后发表声明，宣布终止与D&amp;amp;G的合作。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;迪丽热巴工作室发布的声明称：&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote readability=&quot;7&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;strong&gt;“我司作为中华人民共和国企业，迪丽热巴女士作为中华人民共和国公民，对此事感到无比愤慨!已向Dolce &amp;amp; Gabbana品牌方发出函告：自今日起，我司迪丽热巴女士终止与Dolce &amp;amp; Gabbana品牌合作”。&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;此前迪丽热巴担任杜嘉班纳亚太地区品牌大使。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;&quot; data-backh=&quot;578&quot; data-backw=&quot;526&quot; data-before-oversubscription-url=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/e7Jp2CicGtKCmLhmuw9zP2ttLNYribo9bAD7zxIGSeQzdDIEbQiaxic2s6nsciaT7kF3I1HVGf8ghsKmcCVSH9nNupQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-croporisrc=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/e7Jp2CicGtKCmLhmuw9zP2ttLNYribo9bAD7zxIGSeQzdDIEbQiaxic2s6nsciaT7kF3I1HVGf8ghsKmcCVSH9nNupQ/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-cropx1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropx2=&quot;517.0266159695818&quot; data-cropy1=&quot;0&quot; data-cropy2=&quot;531.8269961977187&quot; data-ratio=&quot;1.0270793036750483&quot; data-s=&quot;300,640&quot; data-src=&quot;http://img2.jintiankansha.me/get?src=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/RiacFDBX14xC7rrxMCrZND5eHRYgtLdSaRTWjcnaeEv7o5GJEkSK2ib9kRc3ricnZMOT6LurKydjm7YibWvJmrUGcg/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&quot; data-type=&quot;jpeg&quot; data-w=&quot;517&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;王俊凯工作室也宣布即日起，王俊凯及工作室终止与杜嘉班纳品牌的所有合作，并表示合作的前提是平等交流和相互尊重，尊重彼此的文化和历史，祖国不容侵犯，祖国高于一切。&lt;/p&gt;

